Window Generator¶

For split input dataset on qual batches need split them on windows. Will use WindowGenerator class for spliting data into batches

In [7]:
import tensorflow as tf
from src.BaselineModel import Baseline

column_indices = {name: i for i, name in enumerate(train_df.columns)}

baseline = Baseline(label_index=column_indices['Close'])
    
baseline.compile(
    loss=tf.losses.MeanSquaredError(),
    metrics=[tf.metrics.MeanAbsoluteError(), tf.metrics.MeanSquaredLogarithmicError()]
)
In [8]:
